OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScouts 'putting lives at   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frisk', coroner says        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Young lives are being put at risk by   
OL,6, the Scout Association's failure to     
OL,7, recognise the "inadequacies of their   
OL,8, operational practice", a coroner has   
OL,9, found.                                 
OL,11,FThe coroner also found the organisation
OL,12,Ffailed to "accept any accountability   
OL,13,Fand understand any proper learning"    
OL,14,Ffrom the death of Ben Leonard.         
OL,16,FBen, 16, died during a Scout trip to   
OL,17,Fnorth Wales in August 2018.            
OL,19,FThe Scouts said it was working on its  
OL,20,Fresponse to the recommendations.       
